      "unidentified": "",
      "value": "<p>You have trained your body to resist a particular type of damage.<br /><strong>Prerequisites</strong>: Base attack bonus +4.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTypes_ctl00_LabelName\"><strong>Benefit</strong>: Choose one kinetic damage type (bludgeoning, piercing, or slashing) or one energy type (acid, cold, electricity, fire, or sonic). If you choose a kinetic damage, you ignore damage of that type equal to your base attack bonus; this doesn&rsquo;t stack with DR. If you choose an energy type, you gain energy resistance against that type of energy equal to your base attack bonus.</span></p>"
